{% from "icons.njk" import svgicon %}
{% from "buttons.njk" import primaryButton %}
{% from "macros.njk" import scaled_image %}

<div id="pageHero" class="bg-ams-primary bg-hero--art-xmed xmed:bg-hero--art bg-cover bg-top min-h-screen w-full grid xmed:grid-rows-hero-home justify-items-center pt-28 xmed:pt-0"></div>
<div class="w-full grid justify-items-center -mt-16 xmed:-mt-32 pt-8 xmed:pt-12 px-8 pb-16 bg-pattern--ams-grey">
    <article class="w-full grid justify-items-center pt-4">
        <section class="w-full grid justify-items-center max-w-screen-lg">
            <div class="pb-4 px-4 shadow-md xmed:-mt-10 xmed:p-10 bg-ams-white">
                <h2 class="title-display text-2xl xmed:text-5xl pt-4 xmed:pt-0 pb-4 xmed:pb-8 text-center">
                    Ameswell Art Compendium
                </h2>
                <div class="text-center text-base xmed:text-lg leading-6 tracking-wide">
                    Built in one of the most geographically lush and technologically innovative regions in the country, the Ameswell Hotel is situated on the crossroads of major north/south and east/west corridors. Guided by this theme of intersection, the art collection expresses the junction of real and conceptual.    
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </article>
</div>
<section class="w-full grid justify-items-center p-8 xmed:p-0 xmed:pb-16 bg-ams-base">
    <div class="pb-4 px-4 shadow-md xmed:mt-10 xmed:p-10 max-w-screen-lg bg-ams-white">
        <h2 class="title-display text-xl xmed:text-4xl pt-4 xmed:pt-0 pb-4 text-center">
            Explore The Art
        </h2>
        <div class="text-center text-base xmed:text-lg">
            Whether complex renderings of astral images from the Hubble telescope, unlikely settings of Earthly flora and fauna, manipulated bright lights that slice through somber landscapes, or playfully animated reinterpretations of ancient hieroglyphics, each piece in this eclectic collection both reflects and reimagines the natural historic beauty and flourishing creative genius of the Northern California silicon valley. 
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="artComponent" class="grid justify-items-center w-full">
    {% for item in art %}
        <section class="panel w-full"  data-color="{{item.bgImage}}">
            <figure class="max-w-screen-xl m-auto xmed:grid xmed:items-center xmed:grid-cols-2 xmed:py-12 xmed:gap-12">
                <figcaption class="pt-4 xmed:pt-0 px-8 xmed:px-0">
                    {% if item.images %}
                        <div class="flex flex-col xmed:flex-row">
                            {% for image in item.images %}
                                {{ scaled_image(image) }}
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                    {% else %}
                        {{ scaled_image(item.image) }}
                    {% endif %}
                </figcaption>
                <figcaption class="mt-8 xmed:mt-0 xmed:mx-4 p-4 xmed:p-0 
                {% if item.bgImage == 'bg-ams-white' %}
                        text-ams-primary
                    {% elseif item.bgImage == 'bg-ams-main-12' %}
                        text-ams-primary
                    {% elseif item.bgImage == 'bg-ams-main-14' %}
                        text-ams-primary 
                    {% else %} text-ams-white
                {% endif %}
                ">
                    <header>
                        <h2 class="pb-6 text-sm xmed:text-lg font-bold">
                            {{ item.p1 | safe }}
                        </h2>
                    </header>
                    <p class="mb-4 xmed:hidden xmed:mb-12">
                        {{ item.location }}
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4 moreText text-base xmed:text-lg xmed:mb-12">
                        {{ item.p2 }}
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex justify-center pb-4 xmed:hidden text-center">
                        <button class="read-more__btn segment__cta  relative font-serif font-semibold text-xs uppercase
                        {% if item.bgImage == 'bg-ams-white' %}
                            text-ams-primary segment__cta--primary
                        {% elseif item.bgImage == 'bg-ams-main-12' %}
                            text-ams-primary segment__cta--primary
                        {% elseif item.bgImage == 'bg-ams-main-14' %}
                            text-ams-primary segment__cta--primary    
                        {% else %} text-ams-white segment__cta--white
                        {% endif %} ">
                            MORE
                        </button>
                        <!--arrow down-->
                        <div class="toggle-arrow p-1 xmed:hidden">
                            <svg width="9" height="6" viewBox="0 0 9 6" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M0.5 1L4.5 5L8.5 1"
                                 {% if item.bgImage == 'bg-ams-white' %}  stroke="#213e4c"
                                 {% elseif item.bgImage == 'bg-ams-main-12' %}  stroke="#213e4c"
                                 {% elseif item.bgImage == 'bg-ams-main-14' %}  stroke="#213e4c"
                                 {% else %} stroke="white"
                                 {% endif %}
                                 stroke-linecap="round"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </figcaption>
            </figure>
        </section>
    {% endfor %}
</section>